title: Death in Venice (1971)
description:
Be sure and read the commentary file first.
I wish I had done that before watching it for the first time many years ago.
I like Gustav Mahler's music.
I like Dirk Bogarde.
My wife like's the movie better than I do.
Don't ask me why I include the closed caption file since subtitles are included.
Don't ask my why I made the "routine" file, much less why I include it.
It is a good movie.

Enough said.
